data.value: A friend of yours confides in you that they stole something valuablle and sold it so that they could pay for rent, but now feel guilty about it. You promise to keep their secret. Shortly thereafter, a different friend approaches you and says they lost that same valuable thing, and if they don't get it back their family will disown them. You promise to tell them if you hear anything. Should you:
